hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: There's a three month trial period medicinefortherestofus.com I loved the warm bosom of academia, you’ve kind of got an arm around you and I think that’s fantastic. But college isn’t about the bricks and mortar, it’s about the people you meet. Although I kept leaving and doing this that and the other, I did meet some incredible lecturers that really inspired me and helped make the transition from working class thug into what I am today.
